{"tid":1425731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實彭浩翔同余文樂咁博做乜？","createTime":"2019-08-06T20:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:05:47.000Z","uid":5652,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d949d60215bc89ebe07167b562cbb30b396d7052","tid":1425731,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:04:25.000Z","msg":"黃浩翔條廢柴拍開港產片 得啲on9香港人聽2句粗口就好貼地先會買票睇佢 <br />\n佢個名又吸引唔到大明星拍 又冇大6佬投資 <br />\n佢放棄香港市場 有幾多大6佬識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識你都唔會比錢投資你啲垃圾電影啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n余文樂得個垃圾牌子係大6 好似而家已經都唔係好多人買 <br />\n電影都係拍啲低成本港產片先有主角做 <br />\n一拍啲同大6 合拍片已經做大茄 配角 拍賭城風雲 赤道對白都唔多句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放棄香港市場 去大6拍電視劇唔係拍啲大明星都勉強做到主角仔 <br />\n大制作大陸都睇你唔撚起啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢2條無料既好心出少句聲食2家茶飯好過啦<br />\n而家做過街老鼠 阿爺又唔會睇得起你2件廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4ab6d1476991fb2904c98cde9de6555999ec8f","tid":1425731,"uid":166245,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:32:24.000Z","msg":"奶極咪又係二等公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好事就大家都係中國人<br />\n壞事嘅時候就會話係香港人/台灣人做嫁，唔關我哋事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bae6eeff36a88854d285cc7109e42efe0b561f","tid":1425731,"uid":234098,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:42:21.000Z","msg":"我諗係人地迫佢地"},{"pid":"aa8d139362da6eb5d21240a9677aef811d973140","tid":1425731,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:43:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com